Trans Influencer Sentenced To 5 Years In Jail For This
Subscribe Here 👉 http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3w0pdO7

Officials in Cameroon, a country lying at the junction of western and central Africa have just sentenced two transgender women to five years in prison. Human rights activists are saying that this is part of a growing criminalization of minorities and transgender people in the country.
